FOR RUNNING PIPE 4
1) REGISTER fot repeatmasker using this link and download repeatmaskerlibraries-[version].tar.gz from http://www.girinst.org/server/RepBase/index.php
	cp ~/Downloads/repeatmaskerlibraries* /your/repo/location/tools/RepeatMasker/
and type the following commands
	
	cd /your/repo/location/tools/RepeatMasker/
	sudo gunzip repeatmaskerlibraries-*.tar.gz 
	sudo tar xvf repeatmaskerlibraries-*.tar 
	sudo rm repeatmaskerlibraries-*.tar



2) download the nt database from ncbi using this command to the tools/ folder 
	
	wget ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast/db/nt*


	
